This command loggs demotion and promotion as well as makes user aware that he/she got demoted by whom

Command: ?demote

Response
{delete} 
{require:Senior Moderators} 
{dm:$1} {!role $1 -$2+} 
{!announce {#audit_log} $1 got demoted from $2 by {user}. } 
You got demoted from $2 role in {server} by {user}.

Use it like ?demote @user <rolename>
